sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Adapter<br/>(any platform)
    participant R as Agent Registry
    participant O as Orchestrator
    participant K as Kafka

    Note over A,K: Startup — Agent Registration
    A->>R: POST /agents  (Agent Card payload)
    R-->>A: 201 registered

    Note over O,K: Runtime — Task Dispatch
    O->>R: GET /agents?skill=summarize
    R-->>O: [{ name, url, skills, input_schema }]

    O->>K: PUBLISH to agent.tasks.mistral-summarizer<br/>{ task_id, skill, input }

    K->>A: CONSUME task message
    A->>A: call platform API<br/>(Mistral / Vertex / Dataiku / Snowflake)
    A->>K: PUBLISH to agent.results<br/>{ task_id, agent, result }
    A->>K: PUBLISH to agent.events<br/>{ task_id, agent, status }

    O->>K: CONSUME from agent.results<br/>(filter by task_id)
